data.description: WOW!  SINGLE STORY HOME. The location is perfectly set at the towards the end of the Cul-de-sac and nestled in a most serene part of the neighborhood. This very well-kept and loved home features 4 Bedrooms and 3 FULL Bathrooms. The formal dining room could even be converted into a 5th bedroom if needed. The home has beautiful flooring throughout with carpet in the bedrooms. The floorplan is very open and has a bedroom and bathroom on the opposite end of the home from the other 3 bedrooms and bathrooms.  The Large Kitchen with plenty of cabinet space, island/bar, breakfast nook and pantry, opens to the Family room where you can warm your toes by the fireplace on those cold winter nights. The windows are dual pane allowing the home to illuminate plenty of natural lighting from outside.  The Master Bedroom has room for you to also have a sitting area for reading. The Master Bathroom has a nice size soaking tub and a separate shower. The AC unit and the Water Heater were replaced in approximately 2021. The back yard is practically maintenance free. There is a nice side yard with endless possibilities to what you could plant and grow.   Managed by an HOA with low dues this community cares about keeping the neighborhood desirable. Take advantage of this opportunity to own this magnificent home in Wildomar (just next to Murrieta). Close to freeways and shopping.
